A. Reflection
What was the most challenging part of the workflow? Why?
The most challenging part was designing the data preprocessing pipeline. Healthcare data is heterogeneous
(lab values, demographics, clinical notes) and often incomplete. Handling missing values while ensuring that
imputation choices don’t introduce bias requires careful thought. Balancing data quality, fairness, and model
readiness was more complex than selecting the model itself.

How would you improve your approach with more time/resources?
With more time and resources, I would:

Expand the dataset by collaborating with multiple hospitals to improve generalizability.

Incorporate unstructured data (e.g., clinician notes) using NLP for richer features.

Deploy fairness audits and bias-mitigation techniques iteratively.

Build interactive dashboards for clinicians to visualize predictions and explanations in real time.

B. Diagram
AI Development Workflow (based on CRISP-DM framework):

┌─────────────────────────────┐
   │ 1. Problem Definition       │
   │ - Define objectives         │
   │ - Identify stakeholders     │
   └─────────────┬───────────────┘
                 │
   ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐
   │ 2. Data Collection           │
   │ - Gather EHR, demographics  │
   │ - Ensure privacy compliance │
   └─────────────┬───────────────┘
                 │
   ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐
   │ 3. Data Preprocessing        │
   │ - Clean & impute missing    │
   │ - Feature engineering       │
   │ - Normalize/encode          │
   └─────────────┬───────────────┘
                 │
   ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐
   │ 4. Model Development         │
   │ - Train/test split           │
   │ - Select & tune model        │
   │ - Cross-validation           │
   └─────────────┬───────────────┘
                 │
   ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐
   │ 5. Evaluation                │
   │ - Accuracy, Precision, Recall│
   │ - Fairness checks            │
   └─────────────┬───────────────┘
                 │
   ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐
   │ 6. Deployment                │
   │ - Integrate with hospital IT │
   │ - Monitor concept drift      │
   │ - Ensure regulatory (HIPAA) │
   └─────────────┬───────────────┘
                 │
   ┌─────────────▼───────────────┐
   │ 7. Monitoring & Feedback     │
   │ - Clinician-in-loop reviews │
   │ - Continuous retraining     │
   └─────────────────────────────┘
